Subject: [PATCH v16 6/6] remoteproc: stm32: Add support of an OP-TEE TA to load the firmware
Date: Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:58:33 +0100
Message-ID: <20250325095833.3059895-7-arnaud.pouliquen@foss.st.com>
